lead_paragraph: Beyonce proved once again she is the contemporary rock star, and she used the MTV Video Music Awards stage to showcase her skills and outshine her peers, from Rihanna to Britney Spears.

headline.main: Beyonce Proves She's in a Lane of Her Own at MTV VMAs
